# Core Purity (FC/IS)

These files are the **functional core**. They must stay pure.

- **No Effect** — no `Effect.gen`, `Effect.run*`, `Effect.log`, or any Effect API
- **No I/O** — no fetch, fs, process, or external calls
- **Return** — `Result` for sync validation; plain values otherwise
- **Shell boundary** — Shell in `src/shell/*.ts` uses `Effect.fromResult` when calling core
